content: wtfsayo: Merged 14 PRs this week with significant contributions to core functionality, including major refactoring of types and registry validation in #3436 (+1445/-824 lines) and character methods in #3400 (+3208/-4660 lines). Added several new features and improvements such as Anthropic local embedding (#3474), agent commands (#3424), and expanded test coverage across multiple components (OpenAI, Anthropic, SQLite). Maintained consistent daily activity with substantial code changes (+24.7k/-22.2k lines total), focusing primarily on code improvements, feature additions, and build system fixes.
